    <entry>
      <title>统计学之无偏估计</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/04/%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%A0%E5%81%8F%E4%BC%B0%E8%AE%A1-%E5%9D%87%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%B9%E5%B7%AE/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/04/%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%A0%E5%81%8F%E4%BC%B0%E8%AE%A1-%E5%9D%87%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%B9%E5%B7%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-简介"><a href="#1-简介" class="headerlink" title="1. 简介"></a>1. 简介</h2><p>估计量的数学期望等于被估计参数的真实值，则称此估计量为被估计参数的<strong>无偏估计</strong>，即具有无偏性，是一种用于评价被评估量优良性的准则。<strong>无偏估计的意义是：在多次重复采样下，它们的平均数接近所估计参数真值</strong>。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="2-均值与方差"><a href="#2-均值与方差" class="headerlink" title="2. 均值与方差"></a>2. 均值与方差</h2><p>设随机变量<script type="math/tex">X</script>的期望为<script type="math/tex">\mu</script>，方差为<script type="math/tex">\sigma^2</script>，即：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}     \mu & = E ( X )  \\  \sigma ^ { 2 } & = E ( X - \mu ) ^ { 2  } \end{aligned}</script><p>现实应用中<script type="math/tex">X</script>的分布往往难以获知，但可以通过采样的方式估计，用<script type="math/tex">S ^ { 2 }</script>估计<script type="math/tex">\sigma^2</script>：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S ^ { 2 } = \frac { 1 } { n } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 }</script><p>而现实中往往连<script type="math/tex">X</script>的期望<script type="math/tex">\mu</script>也未知，但通过采样可以得到样本的均值<script type="math/tex">\overline { X }</script>：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\overline { X } = \frac { 1 } { n } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } X _ { i }\</script><p>并且均值<script type="math/tex">\overline { X }</script>是<script type="math/tex">X</script>的无偏估计。<br>推导过程：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}E \overline { X } & = \frac { 1 } { n } \left( E X _ { 1 } + E X _ { 2 } + \cdots + E X _ { n } \right) = \frac { 1 } { n } ( \mu + \mu + \cdots + \mu ) =\mu \\\operatorname { Var } (\overline { X }) & = \frac { 1 } { n ^ { 2 } } \left( \operatorname { Var } \left( X _ { 1 } \right) + \operatorname { Var } \left( X _ { 2 } \right) + \cdots + \operatorname { Var } \left( X _ { n } \right) \right) = \frac { 1 } { n } \sigma^2\end{aligned}</script><p>则<script type="math/tex">S ^ { 2 }</script>为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S ^ { 2 } = \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \overline{X} \right) ^ { 2 }</script><p>并且<script type="math/tex">S ^ { 2 }</script>是<script type="math/tex">\sigma^2</script>无偏估计。</p><p>推导过程：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned} \mathrm { E } \left[ S ^ { 2 } \right] & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \overline { X } \right) ^ { 2 } \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) - ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \right) ^ { 2 } \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - 2 ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) + ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right) \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - \frac { 2 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) + \frac { 1 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } 1 \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - \frac { 2 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) + \frac { 1 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \cdot n \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - \frac { 2 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) + \frac{n}{n-1}( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right]\end{aligned}</script><p>其中：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\overline { X } - \mu = \frac { 1 } { n } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } X _ { i } - \mu = \frac { 1 } { n } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } X _ { i } - \frac { 1 } { n } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \mu = \frac { 1 } { n } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right)</script><p>于是：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned} \mathrm { E } \left[ S ^ { 2 } \right] & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - \frac { 2 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) + \frac{n}{n-1}( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - \frac { 2 } { n-1 } ( \overline { X } - \mu ) \cdot n \cdot ( \overline { X } - \mu ) + \frac{n}{n-1}( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } - \frac{n}{n-1} ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 }  \right] \\ & = \mathrm { E } \left[ \frac { 1 } { n-1 } \sum _ { i = 1 } ^ { n } \left( X _ { i } - \mu \right) ^ { 2 } \right] - \frac{n}{n-1}\mathrm { E } \left[ ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right] \\ & = \frac{n}{n-1}\sigma ^ { 2 } - \mathrm { E } \left[ ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right] \end{aligned}</script><p>又：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathrm { E } \left[ ( \overline { X } - \mu ) ^ { 2 } \right] =\operatorname { Var } (\overline { X })= \frac { 1 } { n } \sigma ^ { 2 }</script><p>得到：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathrm { E } \left[ S ^ { 2 } \right] = \frac{n}{n-1}\sigma ^ { 2 } - \frac { 1 } { n } \sigma ^ { 2 }= \sigma ^ { 2 }</script><p>能通过实验验证吗？<strong>高斯分布</strong><br>参考：<a href="https://www.matongxue.com/madocs/607.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.matongxue.com/madocs/607.html</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
